\left.=\left(y^{(1)}, \ldots, y^{(n)}\right)\right\}= \\
=\prod_{k=1}^{n} q\left(y_{1}^{(k)}, \ldots, y_{s}^{(k)} ; \tilde{y}_{1}^{(k)}, \ldots, \tilde{y}_{r}^{(k)}\right)
